node.text:
Come on Barbie, let’s go party...🩺💉🩸🦠

And by that we mean endless hours over the past 1.5 years (feels like eternity) learning about, caring for, and attempting to prevent all things COVID. 

Honored to have so many of our #womeninmedicine transformed into @barbie dolls. We know this does not represent *all* types of women in medicine, but an incredible step in the right direction and tremendously encouraging role models for kids (& adults) everywhere! 

Proud #womeninmedicine 
#womenempowerment #womeninstem #healthcareheroes 

@womeninmedicine 
@barbie @mattel

We see years of dedication, determination, sleep deprivation, and everything in between! 💤📟 We love seeing our women dominate in all fields, but especially in those where we are underrepresented! 

We are #womeninmedicine and SO proud! #mondaymotivation #whatasurgeonlookslike #womenempoweringwomen #medicine #transplantsurgeon #boss 

Congrats @chloewangmd @womeninmedicine

We are #womeninmedicine #womenempowerment #diversityandinclusion #minoritiesinmedicine #makeithappen #leaders #thisfemphysiciancan #orthopedics

node.text:
Summer Giveaway!! 🌴☀️💦

We love sharing the quarterly @stethishop boxes with you - and this breezy summer box hits the spot! 

Filled with: 
1. Posh pink Satin pillow case (my fave for preventing hair damage!) 
2. Stethi chic water bottle 
3. Collagen hydrogel under eye masks x 2 
4. Jergens ultra healing lotion - thank you excess use of sanitizer the past year 
5. New Day Organics citrus grove deodorant 

We’re giving away a box to one of you with super simple rules: 
 ▪️Follow @womeninmedicine
 ▪️Follow @stethishop
 ▪️Tag a friend! 

The winner will receive this quarters box! Giveaway ends on July 11th. Winner randomly selected and announced shortly thereafter!  #womeninmedicine

Virtual celebrations for getting through your first week!! 🎈Everyone from our students, interns, to our newly minted attendings - you’ve survived! Keep learning, keep growing!! 

We are #womeninmedicine #womenempowerment #healthcare #newbeginnings #medicine 

Working towards that DPT! @amandalakristine

node.text:
July 1st!! A huge milestone for so many in medicine. 

We know all too well the pressure you might feel, going from the peak of your game days before to new, uncharted beginnings with the switch of a day!

You’ve heard it all before - we’ve all been there, you’ll find your momentum and excel at your own pace. But we’re here to tell you again, savor the moments (good and bad) because they go all too fast! 

We can’t wait to watch you grow! 

@womeninmedicine 
#womeninmedicine #july1st 
#womensupportingwomen
